title: Bobby Went On A Date + Chris Janson Stops By For Friday Morning Conversation
itunes:title: Bobby Went On A Date + Chris Janson Stops By For Friday Morning Conversation
description:
Bobby recaps his 45 minute date. Chris Janson talks about singing with Nickelback in the Friday Morning Conversation. Also, Bobby announces he will be a judge for the Miss America Competition.
